{"tid":977063,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"H小姐 我真係好掛住你 麻煩你入一入黎","createTime":"2019-01-11T01:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T02:15:08.000Z","uid":180460,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6c30688f984d90b52a2222ca31081af9d03b1ac0","tid":977063,"uid":180460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T01:59:27.000Z","msg":"我唔知會唔會有機會你撳到入黎睇<br />\n同你一齊呢幾個月<br />\n由朋友 到令你真係對我有意思<br />\n再曖昧然後成為情侶<br />\n雖然你選擇放手 唔想繼續一齊<br />\n但係我好想話你知我好想要你<br />\n再可以既話 我真係好想同你試下相處<br />\n唔好唔試下磨合就覺得唔夾<br />\n你話你中意出去玩<br />\n我又唔係令你變返乖既原因<br />\n好想你考慮清楚<br />\n無論如何我都想同你捱過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2fb9dadd5b488833703ad956797ee97d3a5f2e","tid":977063,"uid":111625,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"忘記佢啦，佢依加日日比人當狗咁屌緊呀"},{"pid":"0b17131c31eefe75c7339453c4311a1737ff458e","tid":977063,"uid":201640,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"佢講到咁擺明未挽夠，唔愛你啦，真係愛你嘅又點會分手？"},{"pid":"5621f1fe3ea4a377533867b8a95b8cccd7198012","tid":977063,"uid":180460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c2fb9dadd5b488833703ad956797ee97d3a5f2e","tid":977063,"uid":111625,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"忘記佢啦，佢依加日日比人當狗咁屌緊呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:06:02.000Z","msg":"唔好咁啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c6dee5b5b9c7b7e024d61f4e91625b620ef924","tid":977063,"uid":180460,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b17131c31eefe75c7339453c4311a1737ff458e","tid":977063,"uid":201640,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:05:44.000Z","msg":"佢講到咁擺明未挽夠，唔愛你啦，真係愛你嘅又點會分手？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"我覺得係佢藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24d003eb13ca0b3869c37fcde57e129138725fb","tid":977063,"uid"